{"tid":773906,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[仲話香港係獨立關稅區]香港被配上「五星紅旗」　瑞士航空：符合國際慣例","createTime":"2018-08-10T01:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T03:09:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c03de75a56379ac0863d810638f9a4d122c0fcb","tid":773906,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A2%AB%E9%85%8D%E4%B8%8A-%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E7%B4%85%E6%97%97-%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%85%A3%E4%BE%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2585%258D%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2597%2597-%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%2585%25A3%25E4%25BE%258B%2F&d=0QVthNlhK99TeRNrWxp4kKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=e8f37d90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2585%258D%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2597%2597-%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%2585%25A3%25E4%25BE%258B%2F&h=ec4eb720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A2%AB%E9%85%8D%E4%B8%8A-%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E7%B4%85%E6%97%97-%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%85%A3%E4%BE%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國近期向多家航空公司施壓，其中瑞士航空早前已應中方要求，將台灣改為「中國台灣（Taiwan, China）」。近日瑞航再被發現，網站上連香港的區旗都被改成中國「五星紅旗」。瑞航則解釋有關做法是符合國際慣例。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》記者今日瀏覽瑞士航空官方網站，可見網站右上角選擇所在地的欄目中，香港被配上了中國國旗，而非使用香港區旗。暫時未知瑞士航空是何時作出此修訂。<br />\n<br />\n英文網媒《HKFP》引述瑞航發言人Meike Fuhlrott回應指，有關做法是符合國際慣例。報道又指有讀者向航空公司作出投訴，獲回覆指在設計界面時是要符合國際慣例，「包括考慮國際客戶的風俗習慣」。<br />\n<br />\n中國近來要求多家航空公司，在官網中不得把台灣標註為國家。其中瑞士航空早在今年5月，已被發現按北京的要求，將台灣的標示改為「中國台灣（Taiwan, China）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/swiss-01_GDKMK_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fswiss-01_GDKMK_1200x0.png&h=7faa783c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b0b666a50c28d415b674cc135f2382cc0c9b48c","tid":773906,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"又打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d4768d2d14fe3f3448125f74130d5c62fd431a","tid":773906,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"做多左啦"},{"pid":"8844326e2ddcdfb4654443b5e22c7c3b75d68d21","tid":773906,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaf14442d25d7db5cdff45c1a51b61367998eab","tid":773906,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"11d4768d2d14fe3f3448125f74130d5c62fd431a","tid":773906,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"做多左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"做比美國睇，千祈唔好當香港係獨立關稅區"},{"pid":"7934793167212b91afb54f1e2b374460b62a7e98","tid":773906,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"child登仔又要杯葛多一間<br />\n真係忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}